---
title: Chilli & Lime Jackfruit Rice Bowl with Ginger-Lemongrass Veggies & Sesame Seeds
description: Jackfruit marinated with mild chilli and lime – our favourite (and totally irresistible) veggie alternative to pulled pork. Pair it with our tried-and-true rice bowl recipe that requires zero fuss assemblage and it’ll be in the bowl in a flash.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
